from.S: merged.measurement m left join sdkjson.live_pitch_data l on m.measurementid = l.measurementid left join sdkjson.measurement json_m on m.measurementid = json_m.measurementid inner join crosscheck.tags t on t.measurement_id = m.measurementid inner join base.games g on g.game_id = t.game_id

select.S: g.location_id, count(m.measurementid), SUM(CASE WHEN l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime > DATEADD(microsec, CAST(SUBSTRING(CAST(json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime as varchar), 3, 6) as integer), l.time) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END), coalesce(m.visionenhanced,FALSE), AVG(NULLIF(1000.0*CASE WHEN l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime > DATEADD(microsec, CAST(SUBSTRING(CAST(json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime as varchar), 3, 6) as integer), l.time) THEN (CASE WHEN date_part(sec, l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime) - (date_part(sec, l.time ) + json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime) < 0 THEN 60 + date_part(sec, l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime) - (date_part(sec, l.time ) + json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime) ELSE date_part(sec, l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime) - (date_part(sec, l.time) + json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime) END) ELSE NULL END, 0)), SUM(NULLIF(1000.0*CASE WHEN l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime > DATEADD(microsec, CAST(SUBSTRING(CAST(json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime as varchar), 3, 6) as integer), l.time) THEN (CASE WHEN date_part(sec, l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime) - (date_part(sec, l.time ) + json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime) < 0 THEN 60 + date_part(sec, l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime) - (date_part(sec, l.time ) + json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime) ELSE date_part(sec, l.sdkuploadermetadata_receivedtime) - (date_part(sec, l.time) + json_m.pitchsegment_trajectorydata_zonetime) END) ELSE NULL END, 0)), getdate() as date_processed
